Package com.oracle.coherence.grpc

Class PofMarshaller<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oracle.coherence.grpc.SerializerMarshaller<T>
      • com.oracle.coherence.grpc.PofMarshaller<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.grpc.MethodDescriptor.Marshaller<T>
    public class PofMarshaller<T>
extends SerializerMarshaller<T>
    gRPC Marshaller that uses POF for serialization.

    The default MarshallerSupplier implementation is named pof, and will delegate to the default POF serializer.

    If you want to use a non-default POF serializer, simply create a custom implementation of a MarshallerSupplier, give it a name using @Named annotation, and make it discoverable either by CDI or a ServiceLoader.

    Since:
    20.06
    Author:
    Aleks Seovic 2019.09.10
